00:23:02,060 --> 00:23:05,770
- Lift the emergency martial law!
- Lift the emergency martial law!

267
00:23:05,770 --> 00:23:09,460
- Condemn the rotten press!
- Condemn the rotten press!

268
00:23:09,460 --> 00:23:13,570
Disperse!

269
00:23:13,570 --> 00:23:17,230
- Condemn the rotten press!
- Condemn the rotten press!

